OL,6,CStage B
OL,8,GJoin me on an audible journey through
OL,9,Gthe history of electronic audio
OL,10,Gsynthesizers. You'll learn how popular
OL,11,Ganalog synths from the 1970s operate,
OL,12,Ghow to change the sounds they make, as
OL,13,Gwell as how the accidental discovery
OL,14,Gof FM synthesis in 1967 changed the
OL,15,Gsound of the 1980s. We'll cover
OL,16,Goscillators, filters, resonance, and
OL,17,Ghow recent chip decapping and reverse
OL,18,Gengineering efforts revealed the
OL,19,Glong-hidden tricks of clever Japanese
OL,20,Gengineers. Everything will be
OL,22,D]CEMFFAX: The world at your fingertips\
